            "is_prior_year_field": false,
            "draft_value": "* $9 billion for NASA's Science Mission Directorate to restore funding for National Academies' Decadal Survey priorities\n* Sustains U.S. leadership in space science against rapid expansion of Chinese lunar and planetary programs\n* Supports a national aerospace workforce and STEM pipeline following FY2026 budgetary instability\n* Drives economic innovation through a 3:1 return on investment in high-tech research and development",
